item.description:
Intallation  Add the required Cordova plugin  cordova plugin add cleverpush-cordova-sdk  Setup iOS  Enable the required capabilities
 Go to your root project and switch to the tab &ldquo;Capabilities&rdquo;
 Enable &ldquo;Push Notifications&rdquo;
 Enable &ldquo;Background Modes&rdquo; and check &ldquo;Remote notifications&rdquo;
  Add Notification Service Extension
This is required for correctly tracking notification deliveries and for displaying big images or videos in notifications.
 Select File &gt; New &gt; Target in Xcode Choose Notification Service Extension and press Next Enter CleverPushNotificationServiceExtension as Product Name, choose Objective-C as language and press Finish Press Activate on the next prompt Add the following at the bottom of your Podfile

Installation  Install via npm or yarn npm i cleverpush-react-native -S
 Link + install native Dependencies for iOS react-native link
 Install Pods for iOS (may be not needed)
cd ios pod install  Setup iOS  Enable the required capabilities
 Go to your root project and switch to the tab &ldquo;Capabilities&rdquo;
 Enable &ldquo;Push Notifications&rdquo;
 Enable &ldquo;Background Modes&rdquo; and check &ldquo;Remote notifications&rdquo;
  Add Notification Service Extension

Installation  Add CleverPush to your Podfile
pod &#39;CleverPush&#39;, &#39;~&gt; 0.1.4&#39; The latest stable iOS SDK version is 0.1.4
 Enable the required capabilities
 Go to your root project and switch to the tab &ldquo;Capabilities&rdquo;
 Enable &ldquo;Push Notifications&rdquo;
 Enable &ldquo;Background Modes&rdquo; and check &ldquo;Remote notifications&rdquo;
